@model DavidBrowning.Admin.ViewModels.Writing.Posts.PostMetadataViewModel
@using DavidBrowning.Admin.Controllers
@using DavidBrowning.Admin.ViewModels
@using DavidBrowning.Admin.ViewModels.Writing
@using DavidBrowning.Models.Writing;
@{
	bool isEditMode = Model.EditMode == EditModes.Edit;
	string formAction = isEditMode ? nameof(WritingController.PostEdit) :
			nameof(WritingController.PostCreate);
	string htmxTarget = $"#{WritingAdminIds.PostMetadataRegion}";
	string overlaySelector = $"#{WritingAdminIds.PostMetadataOverlay}";
}

<section class="card">
	<div class="card-body">
		<h2>
			Metadata
		</h2>
		<p>Create metadata for a post</p>
		<div class="admin-form-region">
			<form method="post" asp-controller="Writing" asp-action="@formAction"
				  data-post-metadata-form data-slug-editor
				  data-post-metadata-edit-mode="@isEditMode.ToString().ToLowerInvariant()"
				  hx-post="@Url.Action(formAction, "Writing")" hx-target="@htmxTarget"
				  hx-swap="innerHTML" hx-disabled-elt="find fieldset"
				  hx-indicator="@overlaySelector"
				  enctype="multipart/form-data" hx-encoding="multipart/form-data">
				<fieldset>
					<div asp-validation-summary="ModelOnly"
						 class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">
					</div>

					@if (isEditMode)
					{
						<input asp-for="Id" type="hidden" />
					}

					<div class="mb-3">
						<label asp-for="Title" class="form-label"></label>
						<input asp-for="Title" class="form-control" autocomplete="off"
							   data-slug-source />
						<span asp-validation-for="Title" class="text-danger"></span>
					</div>

					<div class="mb-3">
						<label asp-for="Subtitle" class="form-label"></label>
						<input asp-for="Subtitle" class="form-control" autocomplete="off" />
						<span asp-validation-for="Subtitle" class="text-danger"></span>
					</div>

					<div class="mb-3">
						<label asp-for="Slug" class="form-label"></label>
						<input asp-for="Slug" class="form-control" autocomplete="off"
							   data-slug-target />
						<span asp-validation-for="Slug" class="text-danger"></span>
					</div>

					<div class="mb-3">
						<label asp-for="Summary" class="form-label"></label>
						<textarea asp-for="Summary" class="form-control" rows="3">
						</textarea>
						<span asp-validation-for="Summary" class="text-danger"></span>
					</div>

					<div class="row mb-3">
						<div class="col-12 col-md-6">
							<label asp-for="Status" class="form-label"></label>
							<select asp-for="Status" class="form-select"
									data-post-status>
								@foreach (PostStatus status in Enum.GetValues(typeof(PostStatus)))
								{
									<option value="@((int)status)">@status.ToString()</option>
								}
							</select>
							<span asp-validation-for="Status" class="text-danger">
							</span>
						</div>
						<div class="col-12 col-md-6">
							@if (Model.PostStyleOptions.Count == 0)
							{
								<div class="alert alert-secondary" role="status">
									Posts cannot be saved unless a style is selected.
									Create a style before creating a post.
								</div>
							}
							else
							{
								<label asp-for="PostStyleId" class="form-label"></label>
								<select asp-for="PostStyleId" class="form-select">
									@foreach (var style in Model.PostStyleOptions)
									{
										<option value="@style.Id">@style.DisplayName</option>
									}
								</select>
								<span asp-validation-for="PostStyleId" class="text-danger">
								</span>
							}
						</div>
						<span asp-validation-for="WritingTagIds" class="text-danger">
						</span>
					</div>

					<div class="mb-3" data-post-tags>
						<h3 class="h6 mb-3">
							Writing tags
						</h3>
						@if (Model.WritingTagOptions.Count == 0)
						{
							<div class="alert alert-secondary" role="status">
								No writing tags are available.
								Create tags before creating a post.
							</div>
						}
						else
						{
							<div class="scrollable-list-panel">
							<div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-sm-2 row-cols-xxl-3 g-2 tag-list">
								@foreach (var tag in Model.WritingTagOptions)
								{
									<div class="col list-group-item m-1">
										<div class="form-check">
											<input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox"
												   name="WritingTagIds" value="@tag.Id"
												   checked="@Model.WritingTagIds.Contains(tag.Id)"
												   id="post-tag-@tag.Id" />
											<label class="form-check-label" for="post-tag-@tag.Id">
												@tag.DisplayName
											</label>
										</div>
									</div>
								}
								</div>
							</div>
						}
					</div>
					<hr />
					<div class="form-check mb-3">
						<input asp-for="IsFeatured" class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" />
						<label asp-for="IsFeatured" class="form-check-label">
							Mark as featured post
						</label>
						<p class="text-secondary">
							Featured posts will show on the home page and top of the writing page.
						</p>
					</div>
					<hr />
					<div class="mt-8">
						<button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">
							Save
						</button>
					</div>
				</fieldset>
			</form>
			@if (!isEditMode)
			{
				<div id="@WritingAdminIds.PostMetadataOverlay"
					 class="admin-form-overlay htmx-indicator"
					 role="status" aria-live="polite" aria-label="Saving metadata">
					<partial name="_Waiting" />
				</div>
			}
		</div>
	</div>
</section>